the brand's authorization

586
00:20:47,759 --> 00:20:48,720
should be no problem.

587
00:20:48,880 --> 00:20:50,359
I heard Aixinkang

588
00:20:50,440 --> 00:20:52,039
is also trying to get that authorization.

589
00:20:52,799 --> 00:20:54,039
Then we can't let our guard down.

590
00:20:55,160 --> 00:20:56,279
Absolutely not.

591
00:20:56,759 --> 00:20:57,920
Keep a close eye on Zhou Xiaofeng.

592
00:20:58,119 --> 00:20:59,480
I'll negotiate with the brand.

593
00:21:00,519 --> 00:21:00,880
Okay.

594
00:21:04,599 --> 00:21:05,720
Drink the milk tea I ordered

595
00:21:05,799 --> 00:21:06,559
while it's still warm.

596
00:21:07,839 --> 00:21:08,160
Here.

597
00:21:11,839 --> 00:21:12,319
Thanks, boss.

598
00:21:12,440 --> 00:21:13,519
No need to be so polite.

599
00:21:13,960 --> 00:21:14,599
You've worked hard.

600
00:21:17,640 --> 00:21:18,759
About Zhang Diao'e's pulmonary AV malformation,

601
00:21:18,759 --> 00:21:19,960
I checked with Ouyang Da.

602
00:21:20,200 --> 00:21:21,880
There is a fourth-generation vascular plug suitable for her.

603
00:21:22,400 --> 00:21:23,440
It's a little more expensive,

604
00:21:23,680 --> 00:21:24,640
but the outcome is much better.

605
00:21:24,960 --> 00:21:25,480
It causes less trauma

606
00:21:25,640 --> 00:21:26,680
and recovery is faster.

607
00:21:27,480 --> 00:21:28,279
Why not just

608
00:21:28,279 --> 00:21:29,119
operate surgically?

609
00:21:29,440 --> 00:21:30,839
I checked the expert consensus

610
00:21:30,880 --> 00:21:32,039
from the Interventional Physicians Branch

611
00:21:32,039 --> 00:21:32,960
of the Chinese Medical Doctor Association.

612
00:21:33,319 --> 00:21:34,680
It does state that surgery

613
00:21:34,759 --> 00:21:35,240
is no longer

614
00:21:35,240 --> 00:21:35,759
the first-line treatment

615
00:21:35,759 --> 00:21:36,640
for pulmonary AV malformations.

616
00:21:37,079 --> 00:21:38,960
But her case is complicated.

617
00:21:39,079 --> 00:21:40,640
There are multiple lesions and many embolizations to do.

618
00:21:40,880 --> 00:21:41,240
Well...

619
00:21:42,160 --> 00:21:42,599
Fine.

620
00:21:42,680 --> 00:21:43,319
You're Cardiology.

621
00:21:43,519 --> 00:21:44,519
As long as you're confident.

622
00:21:45,160 --> 00:21:45,440
Brother,

623
00:21:45,799 --> 00:21:46,599
tell me once the procedure is scheduled.

624
00:21:46,640 --> 00:21:47,240
Let me know, okay?

625
00:21:47,480 --> 00:21:48,240
This pulmonary AV malformation

626
00:21:48,279 --> 00:21:49,039
is extremely rare.

627
00:21:49,119 --> 00:21:49,960
I want to observe it.

628
00:21:50,720 --> 00:21:51,160
Me too.

629
00:21:51,720 --> 00:21:52,279
I'll go with you.

630
00:21:56,839 --> 00:21:57,359
Can you carry that?

631
00:21:57,559 --> 00:21:58,160
I can.

632
00:21:59,279 --> 00:22:00,200
All right. Here.

633
00:22:01,160 --> 00:22:01,559
Try it.

634
00:22:02,279 --> 00:22:03,640
Seafood congee, Xiaoran's favorite.

635
00:22:03,759 --> 00:22:04,519
Five-star rated.

636
00:22:06,240 --> 00:22:07,000
Have you really thought it through?

637
00:22:07,359 --> 00:22:07,759
You're sure?

638
00:22:08,799 --> 00:22:10,680
It wasn't that I didn't want treatment before.

639
00:22:10,880 --> 00:22:12,000
I just didn't want to cause

640
00:22:12,079 --> 00:22:13,359
conflict in the family.

641
00:22:13,640 --> 00:22:15,240
Now that Zhaobang agrees,

642
00:22:15,279 --> 00:22:16,279
I'll do it.

643
00:22:17,319 --> 00:22:18,880
But after surgery,

644
00:22:18,880 --> 00:22:19,759
you'll need observation

645
00:22:19,960 --> 00:22:20,880
and a period of recovery.

646
00:22:21,079 --> 00:22:22,799
You can't try to get pregnant right away.

647
00:22:23,519 --> 00:22:23,920
You and your husband both understand that, right?

648
00:22:24,559 --> 00:22:26,839
Yes.

649
00:22:27,079 --> 00:22:28,599
He said autumn is a bad time to conceive.

650
00:22:29,200 --> 00:22:30,000
Something about my dragon's lair...

651
00:22:30,480 --> 00:22:31,000
What about it?

652
00:22:31,720 --> 00:22:32,680
That it's leaking.

653
00:22:33,119 --> 00:22:34,720
Right. Leaking.

654
00:22:35,240 --> 00:22:36,240
He said that's why I can't have a boy.

655
00:22:36,559 --> 00:22:37,720
I didn't really understand it.

656
00:22:38,000 --> 00:22:38,279
But he agreed.

657
00:22:38,599 --> 00:22:39,319
Good.

658
00:22:40,920 --> 00:22:41,640
Then we'll proceed.

659
00:22:41,640 --> 00:22:42,359
There's one more thing

660
00:22:42,640 --> 00:22:44,119
I'd like to discuss with you.

661
00:22:44,599 --> 00:22:45,079
Your condition is rare

662
00:22:45,119 --> 00:22:46,240
and has educational value

663
00:22:46,640 --> 00:22:47,839
from a medical standpoint.

664
00:22:48,240 --> 00:22:49,079
So I'd like to livestream

665
00:22:50,319 --> 00:22:50,960
the procedure.

666
00:22:52,039 --> 00:22:53,640
Livestream it?

667
00:22:53,759 --> 00:22:55,079
It's all bloody and messy.

668
00:22:55,359 --> 00:22:56,279
Who would watch that?

669
00:22:56,960 --> 00:22:57,640
Not that kind of livestream.

670
00:22:57,799 --> 00:22:58,839
It would be an internal broadcast

671
00:22:58,920 --> 00:23:00,160
for doctors

672
00:23:00,799 --> 00:23:01,880
and medical students.

673
00:23:01,920 --> 00:23:02,839
We would also strictly

674
00:23:03,720 --> 00:23:04,319
protect your privacy.

675
00:23:04,519 --> 00:23:05,440
My thought is,

676
00:23:05,480 --> 00:23:06,160
if we can share this experience,

677
00:23:06,559 --> 00:23:07,440
it may help

678
00:23:07,440 --> 00:23:08,200
other doctors.

679
00:23:09,000 --> 00:23:09,480
At the same time,

680
00:23:10,039 --> 00:23:10,839
it would also be

681
00:23:11,319 --> 00:23:11,839
good publicity

682
00:23:11,839 --> 00:23:12,839
for our department.

683
00:23:14,359 --> 00:23:14,799
Of course,

684
00:23:15,319 --> 00:23:16,200
there's absolutely no pressure.

685
00:23:16,519 --> 00:23:17,519
If you don't want to,

686
00:23:18,440 --> 00:23:19,519
you can refuse.

687
00:23:20,599 --> 00:23:21,799
It would benefit people, right?

688
00:23:22,759 --> 00:23:23,839
For many people, yes.

689
00:23:26,759 --> 00:23:27,759
Then stream it.

690
00:23:28,480 --> 00:23:28,759
Do it.

691
00:23:29,359 --> 00:23:30,079
Actually,

692
00:23:30,440 --> 00:23:31,200
with so many extra eyes

693
00:23:31,359 --> 00:23:32,519
watching you,

694
00:23:32,559 --> 00:23:33,200
you'll be even more careful

695
00:23:33,559 --> 00:23:35,000
and focused

696
00:23:35,039 --> 00:23:37,000
during my procedure.

697
00:23:37,039 --> 00:23:37,880
That makes me safer.

698
00:23:38,119 --> 00:23:38,960
Right, Dr. Ye?

699
00:23:39,480 --> 00:23:39,839
Do it.

700
00:23:40,720 --> 00:23:41,279
Thank you.

701
00:23:42,759 --> 00:23:43,599
For the livestream,

702
00:23:43,599 --> 00:23:44,640
should I put on makeup?

703
00:23:45,440 --> 00:23:46,200
Your face won't be shown.

704
00:23:48,319 --> 00:23:49,079
Just hearing the word livestream

705
00:23:49,079 --> 00:23:50,480
makes me a little nervous.

706
00:23:51,119 --> 00:23:52,519
I'm actually good at livestreaming.

707
00:23:54,799 --> 00:23:56,839
I won't eat for the next few days.

708
00:23:58,319 --> 00:23:59,039
I'll lose weight.

709
00:23:59,480 --> 00:24:01,519
I need to look presentable.

710
00:24:01,799 --> 00:24:02,400
Right?

711
00:24:09,680 --> 00:24:10,359
Exercise.

712
00:24:11,119 --> 00:24:11,839
Lose weight.

713
00:24:12,880 --> 00:24:14,559
Stop swaying.

714
00:24:15,200 --> 00:24:16,440
You're making me dizzy.

715
00:24:18,319 --> 00:24:19,079
How do you usually

716
00:24:19,079 --> 00:24:20,720
stay in shape?

717
00:24:20,839 --> 00:24:22,279
Look at that tiny waist.

718
00:24:23,000 --> 00:24:24,359
You have a little belly too.

719
00:24:25,799 --> 00:24:26,359
What are you looking at?

720
00:24:28,279 --> 00:24:29,480
Is that your cat?

721
00:24:31,119 --> 00:24:31,799
Look.

722
00:24:32,200 --> 00:24:33,440
You're pretty,

723
00:24:33,440 --> 00:24:34,960
and your cat is pretty too.

724
00:24:37,279 --> 00:24:37,880
Xiaobai

725
00:24:38,440 --> 00:24:39,200
is a ragdoll.

726
00:24:40,640 --> 00:24:41,759
Look at that little face,

727
00:24:41,839 --> 00:24:43,160
round and fluffy.

728
00:24:43,400 --> 00:24:45,279
She really does look like a doll.

729
00:24:46,440 --> 00:24:47,920
She's still a baby.

730
00:24:49,039 --> 00:24:50,640
Sometimes she's clingy.

731
00:24:51,039 --> 00:24:52,200
Sometimes she's aloof.

732
00:24:54,400 --> 00:24:55,200
Usually,

733
00:24:55,400 --> 00:24:56,680
she keeps me company at home.

734
00:24:57,160 --> 00:24:58,279
I've been away lately,

735
00:24:58,279 --> 00:24:59,359
so she must be lonely.

736
00:25:00,279 --> 00:25:00,880
Xiaobai,

737
00:25:02,440 --> 00:25:03,720
do you miss Mommy?

738
00:25:05,680 --> 00:25:07,160
You can talk to her?

739
00:25:07,480 --> 00:25:08,720
She really understood you.

740
00:25:08,720 --> 00:25:10,000
She even meowed.

741
00:25:10,920 --> 00:25:11,720
She's very smart.

742
00:25:12,079 --> 00:25:12,799
Seriously.

743
00:25:13,759 --> 00:25:14,960
I have a dog too.

744
00:25:15,200 --> 00:25:16,200
He's really smart.

745
00:25:16,359 --> 00:25:17,440
Let me show you.

746
00:25:18,160 --> 00:25:18,559
Look.

747
00:25:19,640 --> 00:25:20,799
He's not very pretty.

748
00:25:20,839 --> 00:25:21,640
Just a local mutt.

749
00:25:21,799 --> 00:25:22,880
But he's smart.

750
00:25:23,279 --> 00:25:24,200
He runs around

751
00:25:24,240 --> 00:25:25,160
in the yard

752
00:25:25,200 --> 00:25:26,440
and keeps Tingting and me company.

753
00:25:26,640 --> 00:25:27,599
He can even fetch deliveries.

754
00:25:27,960 --> 00:25:28,359
Look.

755
00:25:28,880 --> 00:25:30,480
Ugly-cute. Pretty adorable.

756
00:25:30,480 --> 00:25:31,039
Right?

757
00:25:31,079 --> 00:25:32,319
Look at that little nose.

758
00:25:34,160 --> 00:25:35,200
What's his name?

759
00:25:35,279 --> 00:25:35,720
Dog.

760
00:25:38,440 --> 00:25:39,680
I know he's a dog.

761
00:25:39,720 --> 00:25:40,880
What's his name?

762
00:25:41,200 --> 00:25:43,440
He's a dog, and his name is Dog.

763
00:25:43,720 --> 00:25:45,160
He's just a village mutt.

764
00:25:45,200 --> 00:25:46,400
Why give him a name?

765
00:25:46,920 --> 00:25:48,079
Once you name him,

766
00:25:48,160 --> 00:25:49,160
you get attached.

767
00:25:49,279 --> 00:25:50,480
Then it becomes hard to deal with later.

768
00:25:51,759 --> 00:25:52,880
Hard to deal with what?

769
00:25:53,799 --> 00:25:54,400
Jiaojiao.

770
00:25:54,720 --> 00:25:55,440
Auntie's here.

771
00:25:55,640 --> 00:25:57,279
The doctor wants us in the office.

772
00:25:57,480 --> 00:25:59,000
What's all this food, Auntie?

773
00:26:00,759 --> 00:26:02,400
I'm not eating. I'm dieting.

774
00:26:04,599 --> 00:26:05,599
Here, your shoes.

775
00:26:07,880 --> 00:26:09,480
You're not fat. You look fine.

776
00:26:09,759 --> 00:26:10,799
Don't diet recklessly.

777
00:26:10,880 --> 00:26:11,240
Come on.

778
00:26:13,960 --> 00:26:14,880
It's her turn.

779
00:26:15,319 --> 00:26:15,799
Where's your mask?

780
00:26:16,000 --> 00:26:16,640
Here. Here.

781
00:26:21,319 --> 00:26:21,799
Dog.

782
00:26:23,039 --> 00:26:23,680
Dog.

783
00:26:24,160 --> 00:26:25,559
Do you miss Mommy?

784
00:26:26,960 --> 00:26:27,599
So mushy.

785
00:26:32,079 --> 00:26:33,319
Jiaojiao's lumbar puncture results

786
00:26:33,359 --> 00:26:34,119
are back.

787
00:26:34,400 --> 00:26:35,359
The cerebrospinal fluid was tested too.

788
00:26:35,920 --> 00:26:37,599
Protein was only mildly elevated.

789
00:26:38,440 --> 00:26:39,359
The cell count was normal.

790
00:26:39,720 --> 00:26:40,799
Pathogen testing was negative.

791
00:26:42,000 --> 00:26:42,799
What does that mean?

792
00:26:43,440 --> 00:26:43,960
The test told us nothing?

793
00:26:44,920 --> 00:26:46,200
Jiaojiao's case is complicated.

794
00:26:47,079 --> 00:26:48,240
Although this test

795
00:26:48,359 --> 00:26:49,400
still didn't identify the cause,

796
00:26:49,799 --> 00:26:50,839
ruling things out

797
00:26:51,079 --> 00:26:52,000
is meaningful too.

798
00:26:55,079 --> 00:26:56,279
What did Neurology say?

799
00:26:56,559 --> 00:26:57,119
Neurology said

800
00:26:57,160 --> 00:26:58,720
the ambulatory EEG

801
00:26:58,720 --> 00:26:59,440
did show

802
00:26:59,480 --> 00:27:00,759
typical epileptiform discharges.

803
00:27:01,319 --> 00:27:01,920
They recommend

804
00:27:02,079 --> 00:27:02,839
either doing another

805
00:27:02,880 --> 00:27:03,559
PET/CT scan.

806
00:27:03,960 --> 00:27:04,240
Right.

807
00:27:04,559 --> 00:27:05,079
That's what

808
00:27:05,119 --> 00:27:06,039
we wanted to discuss today.

809
00:27:06,599 --> 00:27:07,160
PET/CT

810
00:27:07,200 --> 00:27:08,039
is an advanced

811
00:27:08,079 --> 00:27:09,039
diagnostic imaging technique.

812
00:27:09,319 --> 00:27:10,279
And it isn't covered by insurance.

813
00:27:12,640 --> 00:27:13,480
So basically,

814
00:27:14,319 --> 00:27:15,200
you want to scan her

815
00:27:15,200 --> 00:27:16,119
from head to toe again?

816
00:27:17,480 --> 00:27:17,920
Doctor,

817
00:27:18,319 --> 00:27:19,759
you said it's expensive.

818
00:27:20,079 --> 00:27:20,680
How much does

819
00:27:20,680 --> 00:27:21,039
one PET/CT scan cost?

820
00:27:21,079 --> 00:27:21,960
And what if

821
00:27:22,759 --> 00:27:23,799
it still doesn't find anything?

822
00:27:23,799 --> 00:27:24,640
One scan costs several thousand yuan.

823
00:27:25,400 --> 00:27:27,240
And

824
00:27:28,640 --> 00:27:29,160
we can't rule out that possibility.

825
00:27:29,359 --> 00:27:30,759
That's why we need to discuss it.

826
00:27:31,519 --> 00:27:32,519
I told you to be careful.

827
00:27:38,559 --> 00:27:40,200
What's wrong with you?

828
00:27:40,200 --> 00:27:41,440
We'll talk about it later.

829
00:27:48,880 --> 00:27:49,440
Jiaojiao.

830
00:27:50,000 --> 00:27:50,480
Jiaojiao.

831
00:27:51,359 --> 00:27:52,000
Jiaojiao.

832
00:27:53,400 --> 00:27:53,880
What's wrong?

833
00:27:56,640 --> 00:27:57,200
What happened? Look.

834
00:27:57,880 --> 00:27:58,759
Jiaojiao.

835
00:28:05,599 --> 00:28:06,119
Jiaojiao.

836
00:28:08,519 --> 00:28:09,119
What happened?

837
00:28:09,880 --> 00:28:10,839
Jiaojiao.

838
00:28:11,559 --> 00:28:12,079
What are you doing?

839
00:28:12,640 --> 00:28:13,519
Going to the bathroom.

840
00:28:13,599 --> 00:28:14,160
Look.

841
00:28:15,160 --> 00:28:15,759
Isn't that Long Jiaojiao?

842
00:28:20,079 --> 00:28:20,799
Look.

843
00:28:21,920 --> 00:28:23,240
Should we call an ambulance?

844
00:28:24,079 --> 00:28:25,680
Dr. Fang, your latte is ready.

845
00:28:26,119 --> 00:28:26,559
Thank you.

846
00:28:28,960 --> 00:28:29,640
Are you okay?

847
00:28:33,759 --> 00:28:34,599
She's even foaming at the mouth.

848
00:28:34,759 --> 00:28:35,920
That's terrifying.

849
00:28:41,000 --> 00:28:41,559
Make way.

850
00:28:42,640 --> 00:28:43,279
Jiaojiao.

851
00:28:44,000 --> 00:28:44,680
Long Jiaojiao.

852
00:28:58,880 --> 00:29:00,319
Is she having a seizure?

853
00:29:00,640 --> 00:29:01,839
epilepsy

854
00:29:01,920 --> 00:29:02,480
That's horrifying.

855
00:29:02,519 --> 00:29:03,119
So scary.

856
00:29:03,240 --> 00:29:04,559
You should stay away from people like that.

857
00:29:04,640 --> 00:29:05,559
That's disgusting.

858
00:29:05,680 --> 00:29:06,440
That's Long Jiaojiao.

859
00:29:06,440 --> 00:29:07,960
I'm logging off for good.

860
00:29:08,000 --> 00:29:09,079
I hope I never run into someone like that.

861
00:29:09,119 --> 00:29:10,519
Unfollowed. I'm done with her.

862
00:29:11,799 --> 00:29:12,599
What do I do?

863
00:29:17,440 --> 00:29:18,359
Should I respond?

864
00:30:00,400 --> 00:30:02,039
Why are you only getting here now?

865
00:30:02,359 --> 00:30:03,640
The doctor said we'd talk this afternoon.

866
00:30:03,680 --> 00:30:05,000
It's almost dark.

867
00:30:05,160 --> 00:30:05,920
I can't

868
00:30:05,960 --> 00:30:06,759
spend every day revolving around you.

869
00:30:06,839 --> 00:30:07,839
I have to deal with

870
00:30:07,839 --> 00:30:08,799
my work too.

871
00:30:10,480 --> 00:30:11,440
Auntie, these two big ones

872
00:30:11,559 --> 00:30:12,759
are for you and Jiaojiao.

873
00:30:13,359 --> 00:30:13,960
Thank you.

874
00:30:30,079 --> 00:30:30,680
What's wrong with her?

875
00:30:30,839 --> 00:30:31,920
Don't say anything.

876
00:30:37,480 --> 00:30:38,599
Your mother too—

877
00:30:39,079 --> 00:30:40,359
she's gone to help your uncle

878
00:30:40,599 --> 00:30:41,680
look after his grandson

879
00:30:41,720 --> 00:30:42,440
and hasn't come for even one day.

880
00:30:42,680 --> 00:30:44,559
If I stayed here every day,

881
00:30:45,039 --> 00:30:45,759
who would earn the money?

882
00:30:45,759 --> 00:30:46,799
Who would support this whole family?

883
00:30:46,880 --> 00:30:47,519
Fine, fine.

884
00:30:47,599 --> 00:30:48,920
You make the money. You support us.

885
00:30:49,160 --> 00:30:49,839
You're the greatest.

886
00:30:50,160 --> 00:30:50,680
By the way,

887
00:30:51,200 --> 00:30:52,680
isn't it getting colder?

888
00:30:53,160 --> 00:30:54,680
The quilt from Panpan's school

889
00:30:54,720 --> 00:30:55,400
is too thin.

890
00:30:55,759 --> 00:30:56,799
There's a thick blanket

891
00:30:56,839 --> 00:30:57,680
on top of the wardrobe at home.

892
00:30:57,839 --> 00:30:59,079
The next time someone goes over,

893
00:30:59,160 --> 00:31:00,519
have them bring it.

894
00:31:01,640 --> 00:31:03,319
And also, your father—

895
00:31:03,519 --> 00:31:05,759
when he picks Tingting up

896
00:31:05,839 --> 00:31:06,599
on the electric scooter,

897
00:31:06,680 --> 00:31:08,319
make sure he wears a helmet.

898
00:31:08,440 --> 00:31:09,599
Otherwise it's unsafe.

899
00:31:09,759 --> 00:31:11,440
It's already good enough

900
00:31:11,559 --> 00:31:12,839
My child?

901
00:31:12,960 --> 00:31:14,000
Isn't she your child too?

902
00:31:14,880 --> 00:31:16,240
What has Dog been eating lately?

903
00:31:16,759 --> 00:31:17,759
Don't keep him tied up.

904
00:31:17,839 --> 00:31:18,279
It's fine.

905
00:31:18,599 --> 00:31:20,359
Let him run around the yard. It makes him happy.

906
00:31:21,680 --> 00:31:23,119
I said I was having surgery.

907
00:31:24,440 --> 00:31:25,519
You didn't tell me, did you?

908
00:31:25,599 --> 00:31:26,119
Well...

909
00:31:26,480 --> 00:31:28,039
Dog had diarrhea a few days ago

910
00:31:28,400 --> 00:31:29,480
and was in poor spirits.

911
00:31:29,799 --> 00:31:31,480
I had Zhang A-si take him away.

912
00:31:32,039 --> 00:31:33,119
What did he do with him?

913
00:31:35,240 --> 00:31:36,240
What do you think?

914
00:31:37,799 --> 00:31:39,559
He was a sick dog. What else could he do?

915
00:31:40,640 --> 00:31:41,640
Why even ask?

916
00:31:42,680 --> 00:31:43,720
We barely have time for people.

917
00:31:45,880 --> 00:31:46,559
Who has time for a dog?

918
00:31:58,279 --> 00:31:59,039
What's wrong?

919
00:32:02,680 --> 00:32:04,160
Of all times to get diarrhea,

920
00:32:04,200 --> 00:32:05,240
why then?

921
00:32:06,240 --> 00:32:07,039
If I'd been home,

922
00:32:07,119 --> 00:32:08,519
I could've mixed

923
00:32:08,519 --> 00:32:10,119
some human medicine into his food.

924
00:32:10,759 --> 00:32:11,920
We can't even take care of people.

925
00:32:11,960 --> 00:32:13,160
Who could take care of a dog?

926
00:32:15,119 --> 00:32:16,720
Good thing we never named him.

927
00:32:17,000 --> 00:32:17,519
Otherwise,

928
00:32:17,839 --> 00:32:18,799
it really would've been hard.

929
00:34:28,360 --> 00:34:29,800
Why are you crying?

930
00:34:30,559 --> 00:34:32,239
The dog died.

931
00:34:34,119 --> 00:34:35,360
Quan.

932
00:34:35,400 --> 00:34:36,519
The dog died.

933
00:34:37,559 --> 00:34:38,960
Look.

934
00:34:39,400 --> 00:34:42,599
My dog died.

935
00:34:46,360 --> 00:34:47,719
Can you understand

936
00:34:47,719 --> 00:34:51,039
how devastated I am, Quan?

937
00:34:51,360 --> 00:34:54,039
Sit with me for a while, Quan.

938
00:35:05,079 --> 00:35:07,039
Poor dog.

939
00:35:08,119 --> 00:35:10,239
I raised him

940
00:35:10,280 --> 00:35:12,840
from a tiny pup.

941
00:35:13,000 --> 00:35:15,320
And just like that, he's gone.

942
00:35:15,559 --> 00:35:19,000
You cry so loudly.

943
00:35:19,400 --> 00:35:21,360
I'm heartbroken.

944
00:35:27,440 --> 00:35:28,760
His life is over.

945
00:35:29,280 --> 00:35:30,280
He went back to Dog Planet.

946
00:35:33,079 --> 00:35:35,000
He doesn't have to suffer here anymore.

947
00:35:36,840 --> 00:35:37,519
That's not so bad.

948
00:35:41,559 --> 00:35:43,400
You educated people

949
00:35:43,480 --> 00:35:44,639
talk such nonsense.

950
00:35:45,519 --> 00:35:47,400
There's no Dog Planet.

951
00:35:48,440 --> 00:35:50,280
Dead means dead.

952
00:35:51,519 --> 00:35:53,360
It means he's gone.

953
00:35:53,800 --> 00:35:55,119
Then he's gone.

954
00:36:08,280 --> 00:36:09,559
Why are you all dressed up

955
00:36:09,679 --> 00:36:11,320
and coming here in the middle of the night?

956
00:36:12,079 --> 00:36:13,440
Meeting someone?

957
00:36:15,280 --> 00:36:17,079
Did I ruin your date?

958
00:36:24,639 --> 00:36:25,159
Is this because

959
00:36:25,159 --> 00:36:26,519
of those videos online?

960
00:36:28,719 --> 00:36:29,280
I saw them.

961
00:36:34,760 --> 00:36:35,639
Those people...

962
00:36:35,639 --> 00:36:38,159
Let them say whatever they want.

963
00:36:38,280 --> 00:36:39,440
Ignore them.

964
00:36:40,280 --> 00:36:41,199
They don't like us,

965
00:36:41,280 --> 00:36:42,760
and we don't like them.

966
00:36:43,400 --> 00:36:44,719
You've been online for years.

967
00:36:44,719 --> 00:36:45,480
Don't you know?

968
00:36:45,480 --> 00:36:46,360
People just

969
00:36:46,960 --> 00:36:47,760
chase whatever is trending.

970
00:36:47,880 --> 00:36:49,440
Today it's this.

971
00:36:49,559 --> 00:36:50,239
Tomorrow it'll be something else.

972
00:36:50,320 --> 00:36:51,679
Why care about them?

973
00:36:52,480 --> 00:36:54,039
Being sick isn't your fault.

974
00:36:55,599 --> 00:36:57,239
Believe me, with these people,

975
00:36:57,960 --> 00:36:59,239
if I film you now

976
00:37:00,519 --> 00:37:01,079
looking this beautiful

977
00:37:01,320 --> 00:37:02,159
and post it online tomorrow,

978
00:37:02,199 --> 00:37:03,360
they'll say you're better.

979
00:37:03,760 --> 00:37:05,360
Then the whole thing will pass.

980
00:37:05,960 --> 00:37:07,960
This may pass,

981
00:37:08,480 --> 00:37:09,960
but my illness won't.

982
00:37:10,960 --> 00:37:12,360
Brother Xu,

983
00:37:14,639 --> 00:37:16,199
I thought

984
00:37:18,280 --> 00:37:19,119
there would always be someone

985
00:37:23,920 --> 00:37:25,199
in this world who could accept me

986
00:37:27,519 --> 00:37:29,880
and catch me when I fall.

987
00:37:30,559 --> 00:37:31,880
You've lost over a million followers

988
00:37:33,840 --> 00:37:35,159
across all platforms.

989
00:37:42,039 --> 00:37:43,880
Do you know how much damage

990
00:37:44,280 --> 00:37:44,960
that caused the company?

991
00:37:45,000 --> 00:37:46,280
Our competitors are even

992
00:37:46,679 --> 00:37:47,559
using it to attack me,

993
00:37:47,639 --> 00:37:48,760
saying the company exploits its creators.

994
00:37:48,800 --> 00:37:50,000
It's insane.

995
00:37:50,280 --> 00:37:50,920
For now, don't

996
00:37:51,400 --> 00:37:52,119
post any updates.

997
00:37:52,239 --> 00:37:53,000
And don't appear in public.

998
00:37:53,360 --> 00:37:54,599
Jiaojiao,

999
00:37:57,840 --> 00:37:58,599
stop bringing up repayment

1000
00:37:58,679 --> 00:38:00,119
or dividends.

1001
00:38:00,320 --> 00:38:01,199
Let's just part on good terms.

1002
00:38:01,840 --> 00:38:03,199
Don't blame me.

1003
00:38:03,960 --> 00:38:04,880
The whole world now knows

1004
00:38:05,159 --> 00:38:06,440
about your condition.

1005
00:38:06,440 --> 00:38:07,199
You saw yourself

1006
00:38:07,400 --> 00:38:08,159
how humiliating that video was.

1007
00:38:08,159 --> 00:38:09,679
All your commercial deals and endorsements

1008
00:38:10,079 --> 00:38:11,360
have been canceled.

1009
00:38:11,639 --> 00:38:12,360
Clients are demanding compensation.

1010
00:38:12,599 --> 00:38:13,880
You can't expect me to pay that.

1011
00:38:14,039 --> 00:38:15,960
You'll have to bear it yourself.

1012
00:38:16,159 --> 00:38:17,480
After all these years,

1013
00:38:18,000 --> 00:38:18,480
I've been loyal enough, haven't I?

1014
00:38:18,480 --> 00:38:19,960
You...

1015
00:38:20,400 --> 00:38:20,719
Don't say another word.

1016
00:38:20,800 --> 00:38:21,800
You're making me furious.

1017
00:38:23,880 --> 00:38:24,639
You call that loyalty?

1018
00:38:25,559 --> 00:38:26,960
Brother Xu, right?

1019
00:38:28,599 --> 00:38:29,519
I think you're kidney-deficient

1020
00:38:30,199 --> 00:38:31,599
and blind too.

1021
00:38:32,280 --> 00:38:34,159
Is that how a human being talks?

1022
00:38:34,800 --> 00:38:36,400
Is it her fault she's sick?

1023
00:38:37,039 --> 00:38:38,639
Let me tell you,

1024
00:38:39,920 --> 00:38:40,559
all this talk about being ashamed of us—

1025
00:38:40,599 --> 00:38:42,039
you look like a baboon.

1026
00:38:42,159 --> 00:38:43,920
She got sick,

1027
00:38:44,159 --> 00:38:44,880
and all you gave her

1028
00:38:45,159 --> 00:38:46,039
was two thousand yuan.

1029
00:38:46,079 --> 00:38:46,800
Aren't you ashamed?

1030
00:38:46,920 --> 00:38:48,000
You won't short her

1031
00:38:48,320 --> 00:38:49,000
even a single cent.

1032
00:38:49,079 --> 00:38:50,119
If you dare bully her,

1033
00:38:50,360 --> 00:38:51,559
I'll take all my sisters

1034
00:38:51,639 --> 00:38:52,719
and livestream outside your company.

1035
00:38:52,719 --> 00:38:54,119
I'll expose you.

1036
00:38:54,239 --> 00:38:54,800
I'll shut your company down.

1037
00:38:55,039 --> 00:38:56,079
You stupid baboon.

1038
00:38:56,159 --> 00:38:57,119
Stupid baboon! Baboon!

1039
00:38:58,280 --> 00:38:59,639
Baboon!

1040
00:38:59,719 --> 00:39:00,320
Go to hell!

1041
00:39:00,679 --> 00:39:01,480
Did you curse him out?

1042
00:39:04,840 --> 00:39:05,360
Did you curse him out?

1043
00:39:06,280 --> 00:39:07,079
I sent two messages.

1044
00:39:08,760 --> 00:39:09,639
What did you say?

1045
00:39:12,320 --> 00:39:13,639
He was bullying you, and I lost my temper.

1046
00:39:13,719 --> 00:39:14,440
I couldn't hold back.

1047
00:39:15,760 --> 00:39:16,280
Baboon.

1048
00:39:18,320 --> 00:39:19,480
Just look at his profile picture.

1049
00:39:19,800 --> 00:39:20,440
Look at that.

1050
00:39:21,079 --> 00:39:22,159
His philtrum is so long.

1051
00:39:22,199 --> 00:39:23,280
If he's not a baboon, what is he?

1052
00:39:24,480 --> 00:39:25,239
That's definitely a baboon.

1053
00:39:25,719 --> 00:39:26,719
I've never even met him.

1054
00:39:26,719 --> 00:39:28,239
But just hearing him talk,

1055
00:39:28,360 --> 00:39:29,280
I know he's not human.

1056
00:39:29,719 --> 00:39:30,400
And you too—

1057
00:39:30,400 --> 00:39:31,840
you really don't know how to judge people.

1058
00:39:33,559 --> 00:39:34,960
How is he any different

1059
00:39:34,960 --> 00:39:36,079
from those people online?

1060
00:39:37,320 --> 00:39:39,199
At a time like this,

1061
00:39:40,960 --> 00:39:41,599
he says things like that?

1062
00:39:42,559 --> 00:39:43,800
And another thing:

1063
00:39:44,480 --> 00:39:45,960
so what if you lose followers?

1064
00:39:45,960 --> 00:39:46,639
You don't need to care about those people.

1065
00:39:46,679 --> 00:39:48,239
Just care about the people who truly like you.

1066
00:39:49,239 --> 00:39:51,039
If I had that many followers,

1067
00:39:51,760 --> 00:39:53,679
I'd brag about it everywhere.

1068
00:39:53,800 --> 00:39:55,199
Would I let this stupid baboon

1069
00:39:55,239 --> 00:39:56,599
tell me what to do?

1070
00:39:57,039 --> 00:39:58,360
I'd date a different handsome guy every day.

1071
00:39:58,360 --> 00:39:59,679
A different one every day.

1072
00:39:59,880 --> 00:40:01,880
I'd make him stare at my nostrils.

1073
00:40:05,639 --> 00:40:07,000
Why are you crying? Don't cry.

1074
00:40:08,039 --> 00:40:09,519
Let him cry. We won't.

1075
00:40:12,039 --> 00:40:13,199
You're so silly.

1076
00:40:30,760 --> 00:40:33,519
Being sick isn't my fault.

1077
00:40:43,159 --> 00:40:43,800
That's right.

1078
00:40:50,400 --> 00:40:51,079
Quan,

1079
00:40:52,559 --> 00:40:53,599
do you remember

1080
00:40:54,840 --> 00:40:56,679
when we boarded at school?

1081
00:40:57,639 --> 00:40:58,400
We used to

1082
00:40:59,000 --> 00:41:00,679
sneak up to the rooftop

1083
00:41:04,280 --> 00:41:05,599
wrapped in

1084
00:41:06,679 --> 00:41:07,320
that blanket of yours—

1085
00:41:08,280 --> 00:41:09,559
the dark red one

1086
00:41:10,480 --> 00:41:11,920
that blanket

1087
00:41:12,000 --> 00:41:13,880
with the huge, ugly peonies

1088
00:41:14,159 --> 00:41:15,639
Now you're calling it ugly?

1089
00:41:17,679 --> 00:41:19,360
Back then, I said

1090
00:41:25,039 --> 00:41:26,280
I wanted to be a dancer.

1091
00:41:26,280 --> 00:41:27,920
I remember.

1092
00:41:29,719 --> 00:41:30,320
What did you say you wanted to be?

1093
00:41:34,079 --> 00:41:35,280
Do you remember?

1094
00:41:35,280 --> 00:41:36,119
I wanted to be a flight attendant.

1095
00:41:40,199 --> 00:41:42,440
I'd wear a little hat,

1096
00:41:44,159 --> 00:41:45,599
tie a pretty silk scarf,

1097
00:41:46,119 --> 00:41:47,880
put on high heels,

1098
00:41:48,559 --> 00:41:49,920
and pull my suitcase behind me.

1099
00:41:49,960 --> 00:41:51,239
I could fly

1100
00:41:52,320 --> 00:41:53,320
to every corner of the world.

1101
00:41:53,320 --> 00:41:54,800
Look at you now.

1102
00:41:58,239 --> 00:41:59,280
You're even prettier than a flight attendant.

1103
00:41:59,800 --> 00:42:01,280
I really am

1104
00:42:03,119 --> 00:42:05,000
pretty far from becoming a dancer.

1105
00:42:05,000 --> 00:42:06,599
We were only teenagers then.

1106
00:42:10,480 --> 00:42:12,079
We thought the whole future

1107
00:42:12,800 --> 00:42:15,360
was in our hands.

1108
00:42:15,599 --> 00:42:17,199
It still is.

1109
00:42:18,159 --> 00:42:19,440
You're far more impressive now

1110
00:42:19,880 --> 00:42:21,000
than any flight attendant.

1111
00:42:21,079 --> 00:42:22,039
And we can

1112
00:42:23,719 --> 00:42:25,119
fly even higher

1113
00:42:25,159 --> 00:42:26,239
and farther than they do.

1114
00:42:26,280 --> 00:42:27,760
How far can

1115
00:42:31,079 --> 00:42:32,159
someone who has seizures

1116
00:42:33,119 --> 00:42:34,199
from time to time really fly?

1117
00:42:35,719 --> 00:42:37,000
As far as you want.

1118
00:42:37,719 --> 00:42:39,000
Look.

1119
00:42:43,920 --> 00:42:44,320
We'll fly that way.

1120
00:42:46,119 --> 00:42:46,920
As far as we want.

1121
00:42:48,199 --> 00:42:49,199
Beyond the mountains.

1122
00:42:49,639 --> 00:42:50,480
Beyond the sea.
